Candidate Search
This feature will be available for use on event day once your organization’s Attending Representative is confirmed to be on-site at the event. From this tab, your designated Event Portal users will have access to search the profiles of all registered candidates to this event as well as individually download resumes. Job seekers are able to register and attend the event up through the end of the event (3pm in the applicable time zone). Thus the list may grow even after event start.

Job Postings

The link below will have you leave the Event Portal and take you to the RecruitMilitary Job Board where your organization's profile is housed and you may manually post jobs. If your organization has an existing job feed with RecruitMilitary, no further action is needed. Your jobs automatically display.

If your organization does not have an existing job feed with RecruitMilitary, your organization users may manually post unlimited jobs on the RecruitMilitary Job Board for view by job seekers registered to attend the event as well as all job seekers who search the Job Board.

Users with existing RecruitMilitary Job Board accounts will be able to sign-in as usual. New users will need to log in and create a password. Important, if one resets their password on the Job Board, it will reset your Event Portal password as well.
